---
title: Blog
description: My blog where I occasionally post about web development and other bits and pieces from the tech world.
layout: base.njk
---

<div class="container">
        <h1>Blog</h1>

        <p>I occasionally post about web development and other bits and pieces from the tech world.</p>

        <ul class="blog-post-list">
            {% for post in collections.post | sortByDate %}
                <li class="blog-post-card">
                    <h4 class="blog-post-card__title"><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h4>

                    <time datetime="{{ post.data.date }}">{{ post.data.postDate }}</time>

                    <p class="blog-post-card__description">{{ post.data.shortDescription }}</p>

                    <div>
                        <a class="button" data-variation="underline" href="{{ post.url }}">Read more</a>
                    </div>
                </li>
            {% endfor %}
        </ul>
</div>
